Specification for Software
--------------------------

Firmware:
- Runs on Raspberry Pi.
- Actually runs the printer.
- Connects to GUI on front of printer.
- Connects via network or USB to client.

Client:
- Runs on Windows, etc.
- Implements Win8 3D printer driver
- Input STL, etc. (hopefully IGES/STEP eventually)
- Outputs complete print job file w/ part, orientation, settings to Firmware
- Displays print status relayed from Firmware.
